$ sudo dmidecode --> this is query the bios and fetch the info from there.
$ sudo dmidecode --type system  --> Shows the system info
$ sudo dmidecode --type baseboard --> Shows the info for the baseboard  
$ lsusb --> Shows usb devices
$ lspci --> SHows PCI devices
$ lscpu --> Shows CPU info

        or

    /proc/cpuinfo

$ lsblk --> Shows the information about the block device.
